headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Property & Business Discounts
content:
With the Nightclub's main office serving as HQ for all your corporate consolidation endeavors, there's still time to expand your criminal network at a discount with 25% off these select Properties, Renovations & Add-Ons:

- Executive Offices, Garages & Renovations
- Special Cargo Warehouses
- Biker Businesses
- Hangars & Hangar Workshop

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for all the details.
